係反擊黑警既文宣材料<br />\n示威者被補過百人，但到今日都無一個黑警被拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請永恆廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，令人明白抗爭者暴力反抗都係出師有名：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y7uAQAj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7uAQAj.gif&h=7764e468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6tuaAD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6tuaAD.gif&h=1dcd33da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BksGHv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BksGHv.gif&h=e616484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6fwoV4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6fwoV4.gif&h=892ec315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L5kz59v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL5kz59v.gif&h=6e4c68e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNTYOnQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNTYOnQ.gif&h=2d6b3e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nr0gz2S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnr0gz2S.gif&h=f6419a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KBLtok.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KBLtok.gif&h=b8ae447c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員以布袋彈瞄準頭部射擊。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h6jQEvO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k